body:
The following tool files were needed open Cyrus SASL library
used in openldap external. Cyrus SASL library was disabled
in openldap and removed from CMSDIST. Remove unused tool files.

title: [CMSSW_7_0_X] nss-toolfile,nspr-toolfile: remove unused tool files
